@startuml mqtt-data-ingestion
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 250
skinparam sequenceParticipantPadding 15
skinparam sequenceBoxBorderColor #333333

participant "Sensor /\nFile Upload" as src
participant "MQTT Broker\n/ MinIO" as entry
participant "Ingest\nWorker" as ingest
participant "PostgreSQL" as db
participant "run-qaqc" as qaqc
participant "water-dp\nWorker" as wdp

== MQTT Device Ingestion ==

src -> entry : MQTT payload\n**mqtt_ingest/{user}/data**
entry -> ingest : deliver to mqtt-ingest
ingest -> db : parse, upsert observations
ingest -> entry : publish **data_parsed**

== File-Based Ingestion ==

src -> entry : upload CSV to MinIO
entry -> ingest : S3 event\n**object_storage_notification**
ingest -> db : parse, upsert observations
ingest -> entry : publish **data_parsed**

== Quality Control & Alerts ==

entry -> qaqc : deliver **data_parsed**
qaqc -> db : run QC tests, store flags
qaqc -> entry : publish **qaqc_done**
entry -> wdp : deliver **qaqc_done**
wdp -> db : evaluate alert rules

note over entry
  **data_parsed** also triggers
  sensor activity recording
  in water-dp Worker
end note

@enduml
